definition.value: A 3-hydroxy steroid that is 5alpha-stigmastane which is substituted at the 3beta position by a hydroxy group.
A steroid glucosiduronic acid that is 5alpha-dihydrotestosterone having a single beta-D-glucuronic acid residue attached at position 17.
A sulfonium compound comprising 4-methylthio-2-oxobutanoic acid having an adenosin-5'-yl group attached to the sulfur.
